# Graph/Tree Program

This program allows you to load and save a graph. You can generate a tree from the graph.
You can also load and save a tree. .  
You can also calculate the distance from a specific point to the departure point for the tree

## Getting Started

Follow these instructions to compile and run the agenda program.

### Prerequisites

- Ensure you have a C compiler installed on your system. If not, you can install one based on your operating system.

### Compilation

Open a terminal and navigate to the directory containing the agenda source code.

```bash
make
```

### Running the Program

After successful compilation, run the executable:

```bash
./main
```

## Usage

The program provides a menu.
Choose the desired option by entering the corresponding number. Follow the on-screen instructions for each option.

## Notes

- Make sure to enter valid data.

